listInfoByEntity: SELECT srf.srf_form_number SDS, sry.sry_portin_number SPN, srf.srf_identification_type 'TIPO DOC', srf.srf_identification_number 'NRO DOC', sry.sry_nim_cabecera 'LINEA', srf.srf_a_entidades_ent_id 'ENTIDAD SDS' FROM SERVICE_REQUEST_FORMS srf, SERVICE_REQUEST_PORTABILITY sry WHERE srf.srf_a_entidades_ent_id = '55' AND srf.srf_form_number = sry.sry_form_number AND srf.srf_special_cellular_number = sry.sry_nim_cabecera and rownum <= 5;
